OL,3,CJesy Nelson says car containing
OL,4,Cmedical equipment for twin girls with
OL,5,CSMA stolen
OL,7,FThe 34-year-old singer asked for help
OL,8,Flocating the vehicle on Instagram,
OL,9,Fsaying the equipment was needed by her
OL,10,Ftwins Ocean Jade and Story Monroe
OL,11,FNelson.
OL,13,FThe twins have been diagnosed with the
OL,14,Frare condition which causes
OL,15,Fprogressive muscle wastage.
OL,17,F"My car got stolen off my driveway in
OL,18,Fthe early hours of this morning, if
OL,19,Fanyone sees a black Defender reg plate
OL,20,FJJ73SSY.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
