OL,3,CJesy Nelson says car containing
OL,4,Cmedical equipment for twin girls with
OL,5,CSMA stolen
OL,7,FFollowing her twins' diagnosis, Nelson
OL,8,Fbegan campaigning for screenings at
OL,9,Fbirth and launched a petition for it
OL,10,Fto be added to the newborn blood spot
OL,11,Fscreening test, also known as the heel-
OL,12,Fprick test which screens for serious
OL,13,Fhealth conditions.
OL,15,FThe petition has amassed more than
OL,16,F100,000 signatures.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
